name: ele.height
descr: Get the height of the element.  The raw height of the element is returned, independent of whether the element is visibile.

formats.name: ele.height
formats.descr: Get the height of the element in [model dimensions](#notation/position).

formats.name: ele.outerHeight
formats.descr: Get the outer height of the element in [model dimensions](#notation/position) (includes height, padding, & border).

formats.name: ele.renderedHeight
formats.descr: Get the height of the element in [rendered dimensions](#notation/position).

formats.name: ele.renderedOuterHeight
formats.descr: Get the outer height of the element in [rendered dimensions](#notation/position) (includes height, padding, & border) in rendered dimensions.
